        <item>
            <title>2.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 30 Jul 2025 20:15:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Shopify/tophat</link>
            <sparkle:version>39</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>Thanks for using Tophat! This update contains improvements and bug fixes:</p><ul><li>The welcome window has been updated to provide additional guidance and to better detect nonstandard installations of Xcode.</li><li>Fixed an issue that prevented Tophat from installing apps from zipped archives that contained a parent folder.</li><li>Fixed an issue that caused the order of devices and simulators to change unexpectedly.</li><li>Fixed an issue that caused the order of extensions to change unexpectedly.</li></ul><p>Tophat now requires macOS 15 or later.</p>]]></description>
